ockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁講wm個心口無左夠收皮啦<br />\n睇下ca3咪證明左囉，降落傘都無"},{"pid":"38702ed433b671d8374a2c1168ff3a80634250e7","tid":489933,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>falcon對翼跛咗就廢武功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nwm冇得飛都仲有大把炮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁講wm個心口無左夠收皮啦<br />\n睇下ca3咪證明左囉，降落傘都無</blockquote><br />\n收皮易難度問題"},{"pid":"5affef476aa166554bec41d201f79018feecae44","tid":489933,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>falcon對翼跛咗就廢武功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nwm冇得飛都仲有大把炮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁講wm個心口無左夠收皮啦<br />\n睇下ca3咪證明左囉，降落傘都無</blockquote><br />\n收皮易難度問題</blockquote><br />\nca3唔小心打中 擋都冇得擋"},{"pid":"f9ac58d045d7d3e3cf5887225b1e902ef9990212","tid":489933,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>falcon對翼跛咗就廢武功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nwm冇得飛都仲有大把炮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁講wm個心口無左夠收皮啦<br />\n睇下ca3咪證明左囉，降落傘都無</blockquote><br />\n收皮易難度問題</blockquote><br />\nca3唔小心打中 擋都冇得擋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但一中到你就玩完<br />\n另一邊好似ca2咁，無左對翼都仲打得，加上ca3加左紅翼同多d槍幫手<br />\n你唔會覺得wm就咁一個人出黎有得同人打呀<br />\n<br />\n所以只可以講各有長短"},{"pid":"7cf94edb152fab16795586ae1506f0d43579dca7","tid":489933,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多人憎war machine<br />\n但係我揀佢 因為佢真心對tony好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太串柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢著甲打有時都幾型"},{"pid":"909383035706944bec591b0b5edb22a22866f45f","tid":489933,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多人憎war machine<br />\n但係我揀佢 因為佢真心對tony好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太串柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢著甲打有時都幾型</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n件甲咁型，邊個穿都型啦"},{"pid":"d5d8f5c15c8c45b297ccc7c6de12b70948ca2ba7","tid":489933,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>電影版係咪完全冇超能力? 又或者咁問 漫畫版既佢係咪變種人果種style同有咩異能</blockquote><br />\n兩件黑人都係靠裝備，不過Warmachine 最近好似全身大改造變成半人半機器，好似鋼骨咁</blockquote><br />\nfalcon 套裝備個人技術含量高好多喎<br />\n完全冇保護咁濟, 中一槍都收得皮<br />\n<br />\ntony 如果唔係放棄玩BOT, WM 根本仲廢過佢d無人ironman</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未去到咁，件戰衣應該同batman,隊長個d新戰衣咁普通槍或但d的光炮都無事<br />\n<br />\n但佢無包晒全身，同wm個種當然無得比<br />\n加上佢走靈活多變路線，例如紅翼，對翼變型，需要的技術同智識都高，同埋紅翼好似佢整<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWm高火力，你有返d軍火常識，狂射就得，除非你話要控制佢飛好難，但佢一穿就用到好似無訓練過唔覺</blockquote><br />\nFalcon飛得好好睇<br />\n睇佢ca2同隻戰鬥機追 加速變速急墜都好正<br />\nCa3一腳踢架直升機 打lagos d卒用嘅combos又係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過真係有d弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日比人拆翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋佢普通人甲又唔包全身好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e59e07aaf6d29838e8fb6ef53bfe73efff6c78b","tid":489933,"uid":2380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>falcon對翼跛咗就廢武功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nwm冇得飛都仲有大把炮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁講wm個心口無左夠收皮啦<br />\n睇下ca3咪證明左囉，降落傘都無</blockquote><br />\n收皮易難度問題</blockquote><br />\nca3唔小心打中 擋都冇得擋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但一中到你就玩完<br />\n另一邊好似ca2咁，無左對翼都仲打得，加上ca3加左紅翼同多d槍幫手<br />\n你唔會覺得wm就咁一個人出黎有得同人打呀<br />\n<br />\n所以只可以講各有長短</blockquote><br />\n仲可以射下飛彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\