ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>falcon對翼跛咗就廢武功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nwm冇得飛都仲有大把炮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁講wm個心口無左夠收皮啦<br />\n睇下ca3咪證明左囉，降落傘都無</blockquote><br />\n收皮易難度問題</blockquote><br />\nca3唔小心打中 擋都冇得擋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但一中到你就玩完<br />\n另一邊好似ca2咁，無左對翼都仲打得，加上ca3加左紅翼同多d槍幫手<br />\n你唔會覺得wm就咁一個人出黎有得同人打呀<br />\n<br />\n所以只可以講各有長短</blockquote><br />\n仲可以射下飛彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/175639_9eb9cd58b9ea5e04c890326b5c1f471f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F175639_9eb9cd58b9ea5e04c890326b5c1f471f.png&h=1c2c519e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以falcon啱打support做任務多d<br />\nCa3做cap左右手好撚正<br />\n成班一齊出mission<br />\n反而wm火力夠自己其實可以自己打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又未必，佢唔夠靈活，上到前線如果對住d強小小又有返d頭腦的對手，都未必夠，你睇下佢隊長都唔中被佢拆支棒，佢其實似高達入面的雷射大炮<br />\n<br />\n其實二個都係支援型，一個係擾敵同拎情報，一個係高火力支援"},{"pid":"25a7863fa8ab877d19af54f61cff07f3723605c5","tid":489933,"uid":42726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:05:46.000Z","msg":"Falcon 漫畫好似接過棒做Captain America<br />\nWar Machine 喺漫畫有冇做過Ironman?"},{"pid":"e9f3aa99bb943213755080947c5900d27da73f50","tid":489933,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Falcon 漫畫好似接過棒做Captain America<br />\nWar Machine 喺漫畫有冇做過Ironman?</blockquote><br />\n有，早期成日做Iron Man"},{"pid":"732fba1035d05d1e10505e97586723cdb564ad2b","tid":489933,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Falcon 漫畫好似接過棒做Captain America<br />\nWar Machine 喺漫畫有冇做過Ironman?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTony試過俾佢做，原因係新開發想試下有咩問題，簡單d講即當佢白老鼠"},{"pid":"71b7d9f47dbf36b884575011f1f71