 />\n<br />\n應該唔會，講廢黑寡婦同鷹眼咪仲廢，反正要打都係卒<br />\n或者對black order要幾打一<br />\n<br />\n最好show d戰鬥以外的野，falcon咪做偵察機囉岩晒，最好俾佢有埋漫畫的異能，方便佢搵野"},{"pid":"91675b8df63fe5af3c7019a4363cbef73257e04c","tid":489933,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>電影版係咪完全冇超能力? 又或者咁問 漫畫版既佢係咪變種人果種style同有咩異能</blockquote><br />\n兩件黑人都係靠裝備，不過Warmachine 最近好似全身大改造變成半人半機器，好似鋼骨咁</blockquote><br />\n改造都差唔多成十年，後尾正常返<br />\n前排仲死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俾Thano一拳打死真係幾柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a08180106847320522a08ca22122a6e87b6d10f","tid":489933,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>電影版係咪完全冇超能力? 又或者咁問 漫畫版既佢係咪變種人果種style同有咩異能</blockquote><br />\n兩件黑人都係靠裝備，不過Warmachine 最近好似全身大改造變成半人半機器，好似鋼骨咁</blockquote><br />\n改造都差唔多成十年，後尾正常返<br />\n前排仲死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俾Thano一拳打死真係幾柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算正常啦，差咁遠個戰鬥力"},{"pid":"6e8b002b39cc83e383e9cabb03cfa9f51e2652bb","tid":489933,"uid":2380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:29:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好驚falcon iw唔夠打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔會，講廢黑寡婦同鷹眼咪仲廢，反正要打都係卒<br />\n或者對black order要幾打一<br />\n<br />\n最好show d戰鬥以外的野，falcon咪做偵察機囉岩晒，最好俾佢有埋漫畫的異能，方便佢搵野</blockquote><br />\n正常人呢幾個真係好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76d3b43d58fac3a72e951a8ff58062686feebca","tid":489933,"uid":124951,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:30:01.000Z","msg":"falcon型好多,antman個期雖然好柒,但ca3令我對佢改觀~<br />\n同埋wm套甲比邊個著都勁架啦,論技術含量,你試下調番轉叫Rhodey著Falcon套野~"}]}